But I wear size ten.

18
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:13,000
How about green? It's size ten.

19
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
Let me try it on.

20
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:18,000
I'm taking too much of your time.

21
